divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside scraping my windshild and I looked up it came from the east moving west it was not as high in the air that I have seen comercial jets flying it was much lower and moving faster than any thing I ever thought possible it took about a second and a half to pass by.I live about a half mile from the main air port here in okc so it also passed over the airport. If I had not looked up I would have never know it came by it was totaly silent if there was noise it was plenty close to hear it.It was round and had a dull silver white glow to it. It did not streak in with a tail like a meteor it was moving from east to west not that far from the ground.I now know why their are so few photos of these things if I had a camera in my hand there is still no way I could have reacted.
